{
  "stem": "18960.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was always had to be a poor person, at least a poor person, participating, invited to share with us the Sabbath meal.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Usually, we were-- we were getting [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] a-- a guest in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Usually poor people were wandering from one town to another.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And after the Friday night services, my grandfather was picking up a couple of wanderers, poor people, to share the Sabbath meal with us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I remember particularly one wintry night [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where it was a-- a big storm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because we were in the snow-- the snow belt area, with the mountains, the Carpathian Mountains there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were no people, no strangers in our-- in our synagogue.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I looked at my grandfather's face.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was very sad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after the services, I disappeared from the synagogue and started looking in other synagogues for a-- for a poor person.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Luckily enough, I found one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not maybe a half an hour later, 45 minutes later, I came to the house with this poor person in tow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I walked in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents, my grandparents were very worried where I was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's a big snow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That they were afraid that maybe I got stuck in the snow someplace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here I walk in with this poor person in tow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and my grandfather looked at me and I saw tears coming down his eyes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] He was very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sit down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He kissed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He thanked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is one event I'll never forget as long as I live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Usually, the-- the Sabbath service is a very happy-- very happy event.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were singing songs.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
